thread.title: Hans Houbolt
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Hans Houbolt

author: Hans Houbolt
title: Hans Houbolt
text:
I have used Ink station after market products for years now and never had any problems. Even shipping to Norfolk Island was no problem for them.,
I believe the inks used are Hitachi Koki, USA as is the original ink?
Stop the OEM rip-off to subsidise the market share. Great stuff.
